dcterms:title: Rickenbacker 4003 Bass Guitar
dcterms:creator: Rickenbacker International Corporation
dcterms:subject: Bass Guitar; Instrument; Scott Pilgrim
dcterms:description: Classic Rickenbacker 4003 four-string electric bass, known for its ringing sustain, strong treble punch and solid low end, with solid maple body, bound neck, rosewood fingerboard, triangle inlays and stereo output. The same model is used by Scott Pilgrim in the 2010 film.
dctermsisDerivativeOf: Scott Pilgrim vs. the World (film); Scott Pilgrim vs. the World: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack
